headline: PayPal Is Skyrocketing, but Here's 1 Warning Before You Buy the Stock
summary: PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL) is finally starting to attract some bullish sentiment from the investment community.  One obvious warning PayPal shareholders must heed is just how competitive the payments landscape has become.  Visa and Mastercard get a lot of attention because of their duopolistic position in the credit card processing niche.
